- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing): The paper focuses on the optimization of the Covariance Matrix Adaptation Evolution Strategy (CMA-ES) algorithm, which is a popular evolutionary optimization algorithm. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper discusses the use of AI techniques for algorithm selection and hyperparameter optimization. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): The paper discusses the comparison of different algorithm selection and configuration techniques for a specific optimization problem. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering): The paper discusses the implementation and comparison of different algorithm selection and configuration techniques, which can be seen as software engineering tasks.
